  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: fffd5ca6d861ad44982ff43836da8b39, type: 2}
  lines:
  - "\u2026"
  - This, ENTIRE time.
  - Our families, our lives, gone, LOST, TAKEN, FOR SOME FUCKING CULT!?!?!?
  - ALL THE WHILE NOBODY EVER LISTENED TO ME.
  - "I KNEW THEY COULDN\u2019T BE FUCKING TRUSTED."
  - "\u2026"
  - "I got word from the spy, there\u2019s an operation underway, they\u2019re stopping
    these inhuman freaks."
  - Bringing them justice, for what they took from us.
  - "The justice I\u2019ve been waiting my entire fucking life for."
  - "He\u2019ll be in contact, get us somewhere safe whilst they get the job done."
